com.cisco.dvbu.ps.deploytool.gui.core.module.data_source

Class DataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cisco.dvbu.ps.deploytool.gui.core.module.data_source.DataSource

  • public class DataSource
extends java.lang.Object

    Bean object for data source module data source records. Intended to be serialized/deserialized by Jackson into/from JSON.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Calvin Goodrich
